My sister has a company Centrum dobrej książki i gry.
"bookshop" will be an online shop for her.

There are books, games and accessories.
Books and games have categories and subcategories, accessories have only categories.

There are 3 types of accounts, for individual customers, companies and library or school. All customers can add many addresses which can be choosen as delivery address at the end of the orders. If library or school type was choosen they can add their payers for example city ​​council. 

Application have Admin Panel, where You can add some products, their categories or publishers and pictures for products.
